{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1739266675\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1739266675\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sky Combat is a fast-paced WWII aviation game where you race to the finish in iconic fighter planes. Use powerups like machine guns, missiles, and boosters to outmaneuver opponents in thrilling air battles. Speed and strategy will decide the winner!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/MST_Title_01_b_w.png?t=1739266675\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/number_one-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1739266675\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Sky Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sky Combat delivers an exhilarating WWII aviation experience with high-speed aerial combat and thrilling races. In single-player mode, you can compete in championships, arcade races, or time trials across various circuits, all set in the skies of iconic WWII battlefields.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/MST_Title_06_b_w.png?t=1739266675\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225030/extras/number_two-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1739266675\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p 